FBIS4-56351 "drlat085_a_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-085 Daily Report 3 May 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba ANPP Special Session Continues in Havana ANPP Special Session Continues in Havana Castro Announces Upcoming Decree FL0305010894 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in Spanish 0000 GMT 3 May 94 FL0305010894 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks Spanish BFN [Excerpt] The National Assembly of the People's Government [ANPP] has approved the policies guiding the national financial reorganization. Commander in Chief Fidel Castro announced the upcoming promulgation of a decree law confiscating ill-gotten wealth resulting from profiteering. [Begin Castro recording] Of course, the first one is going to come out, I believe, this very week. It is a Council of State decree law regarding the confiscation of ill-gotten wealth. [applause] [end recording] [passage omitted]
